title: Neff North Vs. South:  Skate Park Of Tampa
description: If you haven't heard of Skate Park of Tampa, maybe it's time for you to be introduced to skateboarding. Home of the contest of all contests, or session of all sessions, SPoT can be described as the mecca of skateboarding. SPoT's shop opened up in 1993, and its location requires no description to fluff it up. Peep the video and have some respect.
